# Rule based chatbot
## Description:
this project is a simple Rule-based chatbot developed using python.the chatbot respond to user inputs on predefined rules and patterns.

## features:
responds to greeting and common questions
uses predefined rules for conversation 
easy to understand and modify
beginner friendly AI project

## technologies used:
python
## how it work:
the chatbot matches user input with predefined keywords and returns the corresponding response. if no matching rule is found, it provides a default response.
## example:
user: hello
bot:hi! how can i help you.
user: what is your name?
bot: I am a rule based chatbot.
user: bye
bot: goodbye! have a nice day.

## learning outcomes:
understanding rule based AI systems
working with conditional statements
user input handling in python
basic chatbot development concepts
